<inglise> COMMISSION REGULATION (EC) No 2095/98 of 30 September 1998 fixing the estimated production of olive oil and the amount of the unit production aid that may be paid in advance for the 1997/98 marketing year </inglise>
<eesti> KOMISJONI M&Auml;&Auml;RUS (E&Uuml;) nr 2095/98, milles m&auml;&auml;ratakse kindlaks oliivi&otilde;li hinnanguline toodang ja v&otilde;imaliku ettemakstava tootmistoetuse m&auml;&auml;r &uuml;hiku kohta majandusaastaks 1997/98 30. september 1998 </eesti>
<inglise> THE COMMISSION OF THE EUROPEAN COMMUNITIES, </inglise>
<eesti> EUROOPA &Uuml;HENDUSTE KOMISJON, </eesti>
<inglise> Having regard to the Treaty establishing the European Community, </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse Euroopa &Uuml;henduse asutamislepingut, </eesti>
<inglise> Having regard to Council Regulation No 136/66/EEC of 22 September 1966 on the establishment of a common organisation of the market in oils and fats (1), as last amended by Regulation (EC) No 1638/98 (2), </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse n&otilde;ukogu 22. septembri 1966. aasta m&auml;&auml;rust nr 136/66/EM&Uuml; &otilde;li- ja rasvaturu &uuml;hise korralduse kehtestamise kohta, (1) viimati muudetud m&auml;&auml;rusega (E&Uuml;) nr 1638/98, (2) </eesti>
<inglise> Having regard to Council Regulation (EEC) No 2261/84 of 17 July 1984 laying down general rules on the granting of aid for the production of olive oil and of aid to olive oil producer organisations (3), as last amended by Regulation (EC) No 1639/98 (4), and in particular Article 17a(2) thereof, </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse n&otilde;ukogu 17. juuli 1984. aasta m&auml;&auml;rust (EM&Uuml;) nr 2261/84, milles s&auml;testatakse oliivi&otilde;li tootmiseks antava abi ja oliivi&otilde;li tootjate organisatsioonidele antava abi &uuml;ldised eeskirjad, (3) viimati muudetud m&auml;&auml;rusega (E&Uuml;) nr 1639/98, (4) eriti selle artikli 17a l&otilde;iget 2, </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas Article 5 of Regulation No 136/66/EEC provides that the unit production aid must be reduced where the actual production in a given marketing year exceeds the guaranteed maximum quantity fixed for that marketing year; whereas, however, producers whose average production does not amount to 500 kilograms of olive oil per marketing year are not affected by such a reduction; </inglise>
<eesti> ning arvestades, et: m&auml;&auml;ruse nr 136/66/EM&Uuml; artiklis 5 s&auml;testatakse, et tootmistoetuse m&auml;&auml;ra &uuml;hiku kohta peab v&auml;hendama, kui asjaomase turustusaasta tegelik toodang &uuml;letab k&otilde;nealuse turustusaasta jaoks kindlaksm&auml;&auml;ratud garanteeritud maksimumkogust; see v&auml;hendamine ei m&otilde;juta siiski tootjaid, kelle keskmine toodang on v&auml;iksem kui 500 kilogrammi oliivi&otilde;li turustusaasta kohta; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas Article 17a of Regulation (EEC) No 2261/84 provides that in order to determine the unit amount of the production aid for olive oil that can be paid in advance, the estimated production for the marketing year concerned should be determined; whereas that amount must be fixed at a level avoiding any risk of unwarranted payment to olive growers; </inglise>
<eesti> m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 2261/84 artiklis 17a s&auml;testatakse, et oliivi&otilde;li ettemakstava tootmistoetuse m&auml;&auml;ra kindlaksm&auml;&auml;ramiseks &uuml;hiku kohta tuleks kindlaks m&auml;&auml;rata asjaomase turustusaasta hinnanguline toodang; see m&auml;&auml;r tuleb kindlaks m&auml;&auml;rata sellisel tasemel, et v&auml;lditakse oliivikasvatajatele p&otilde;hjendamatute maksete tegemist; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas, in order to establish the estimated production, the Member States must forward to the Commission the data for the olive oil production estimates for each marketing year; whereas the Commission may avail itself of other sources of information; </inglise>
<eesti> hinnangulise toodangu kehtestamiseks peavad liikmesriigid edastama komisjonile andmed oliivi&otilde;li kalkuleeritud toodangu kohta igal turustusaastal; komisjon v&otilde;ib kasutada teisi teabeallikaid; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas the amount of the advance withheld for the establishment of the register of olive cultivation provided for in Council Regulation (EEC) No 2159/92 (5) and the amount withheld for measures to improve the quality of olive oil provided for in Council Regulation (EC) No 1414/97 (6) must be taken into account; </inglise>
<eesti> arvesse tuleb v&otilde;tta n&otilde;ukogu m&auml;&auml;ruses (EM&Uuml;) nr 2159/92 (5) s&auml;testatud oliiviregistri sisseseadmise ja n&otilde;ukogu m&auml;&auml;ruses (E&Uuml;) nr 1414/97 (6) s&auml;testatud oliivi&otilde;li kvaliteedi parandamise meetmete t&otilde;ttu kinnipeetavaid ettemakse summasid; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas the measures provided for in this Regulation are in accordance with the opinion of the Management Committee for Oils and Fats, </inglise>
<eesti> k&auml;esoleva m&auml;&auml;rusega etten&auml;htud meetmed on koosk&otilde;las &otilde;li- ja rasvaturu korralduskomitee arvamusega, </eesti>
<inglise> HAS ADOPTED THIS REGULATION: </inglise>
<eesti> ON VASTU V&Otilde;TNUD K&Auml;ESOLEVA M&Auml;&Auml;RUSE. </eesti>
<inglise> Article 1 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 1 </eesti>
<inglise> For the 1997/98 marketing year the estimated production shall be 2 290 600 tonnes, and the unit amount of the production aid that may be paid in advance shall be ECU 72,53 per 100 kilograms. </inglise>
<eesti> 1997/98. turustusaastal on hinnanguline toodang 2 290 600 tonni ja v&otilde;imalik ettemakstav tootmistoetuse m&auml;&auml;r &uuml;hiku kohta 72,53 ek&uuml;&uuml;d 100 kilogrammi kohta. </eesti>
<inglise> Article 2 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 2 </eesti>
<inglise> This Regulation shall enter into force on the third day following its publication in the Official Journal of the European Communities. </inglise>
<eesti> K&auml;esolev m&auml;&auml;rus j&otilde;ustub kolmandal p&auml;eval p&auml;rast selle avaldamist Euroopa &Uuml;henduste Teatajas. </eesti>
<inglise> This Regulation shall be binding in its entirety and directly applicable in all Member States. </inglise>
<eesti> K&auml;esolev m&auml;&auml;rus on tervikuna siduv ja vahetult kohaldatav k&otilde;ikides liikmesriikides. </eesti>
<inglise> Done at Brussels, 30 September 1998. </inglise>
<eesti> Br&uuml;ssel, 30. september 1998 </eesti>
